Crispy fried chicken.

41
00:02:54,270 --> 00:02:55,530
Crispy fried chicken?

42
00:02:56,650 --> 00:02:58,300
It's an uncommon dish.

43
00:02:58,440 --> 00:03:00,240
Then I'll give you

44
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:03,850
my secret recipe which is worth a million.

45
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:07,350
Smash garlic and onions.

46
00:03:08,150 --> 00:03:09,030
Soak the chicken legs in a sauce made by pepper,

47
00:03:09,030 --> 00:03:12,460
salt, sauce, rice wine for an hour.

48
00:03:13,060 --> 00:03:16,090
Fry the chicken leg in hot oil.

49
