00:17:49,250 --> 00:17:52,230
Now, she only needs to practice the basic posture and techniques

279
00:17:52,230 --> 00:17:53,890
and pretend to be a qin player.

280
00:17:54,300 --> 00:17:57,580
Who will be the one to play the two-man act?

281
00:18:18,830 --> 00:18:20,720
-Bravo!
-So pleasant to the ear.

282
00:18:20,850 --> 00:18:23,990
Cheng Manyi, no wonder you're the World's Greatest Talented Woman.

283
00:18:23,990 --> 00:18:27,430
Bravo! Bravo! Bravo!

284
00:18:30,080 --> 00:18:32,080
I will report to Father

285
00:18:33,120 --> 00:18:35,770
about Vice Censor-in-Chief Du's misbehavior today.

286
00:18:35,770 --> 00:18:38,150
I'd like to see if you can still

287
00:18:38,180 --> 00:18:39,540
be in your position.

288
00:18:40,900 --> 00:18:41,430
Let's go.

289
00:18:46,470 --> 00:18:50,390
Bravo! Bravo! Bravo!

290
00:18:50,890 --> 00:18:53,950
[A Talented Girl Grows Up]

291
00:18:57,540 --> 00:18:58,330
Here.

292
00:19:08,130 --> 00:19:11,830
Did you see Old Crow's face today?

293
00:19:12,170 --> 00:19:14,560
He was really furious.

294
00:19:16,640 --> 00:19:19,910
I didn't expect you to come up with such a trick.

295
00:19:20,270 --> 00:19:21,660
Good for you.

296
00:19:22,090 --> 00:19:26,200
That's called being smart and resourceful.

297
00:19:26,430 --> 00:19:28,260
It's almost the same.

298
00:19:28,910 --> 00:19:32,230
Stop lecturing at a time like this.

299
00:19:33,150 --> 00:19:36,070
I'll help you next time when you're in trouble.

300
00:19:36,850 --> 00:19:39,170
Cheers.

301
00:19:45,140 --> 00:19:47,610
I am not like you.

302
00:19:47,830 --> 00:19:49,650
That won't happen to me.

303
00:19:50,380 --> 00:19:51,270
Yes.

304
00:19:53,510 --> 00:19:56,440
You never lose your temper

305
00:19:56,460 --> 00:19:58,020
and always look serious.

306
00:19:58,060 --> 00:20:02,460
You never make mistakes and always look aloof.

307
00:20:03,070 --> 00:20:06,920
In terms of living a boring life,

308
00:20:07,980 --> 00:20:11,480
you are surely my teacher.

309
00:20:12,300 --> 00:20:13,700
I am flattered.

310
00:20:14,400 --> 00:20:15,460
In other words,

311
00:20:15,810 --> 00:20:17,690
think twice before you make a decision.

312
00:20:17,690 --> 00:20:19,190
Don't be impulsive.

313
00:20:19,550 --> 00:20:21,350
If you can be more intelligent,

314
00:20:21,980 --> 00:20:24,030
you won't

315
00:20:24,270 --> 00:20:27,830
cause countless troubles,

316
00:20:27,910 --> 00:20:31,250
be it minor or serious.

317
00:20:45,210 --> 00:20:47,410
You look handsome when you smile.

318
00:20:50,000 --> 00:20:52,350
Remember to smile more.

319
00:20:53,220 --> 00:20:55,350
It's tiring to be serious all the time.

320
00:20:59,240 --> 00:21:02,470
I've been asked

321
00:21:02,670 --> 00:21:05,670
to be disciplined and behave myself since I was young.

322
00:21:06,350 --> 00:21:10,140
My father stopped me from practicing martial arts.

323
00:21:10,290 --> 00:21:12,220
I couldn't engage with this world.

324
00:21:12,790 --> 00:21:16,980
Although I might be considered as a scholar now,

325
00:21:18,340 --> 00:21:21,180
I haven't found out

326
00:21:21,210 --> 00:21:22,670
who framed the Wen family.

327
00:21:23,730 --> 00:21:26,500
What's worse, I've been suffering from strange illness,

328
00:21:26,500 --> 00:21:28,220
which made my parents worry.

329
00:21:29,630 --> 00:21:32,730
That's why I am here.

330
00:21:33,750 --> 00:21:36,850
I will teach you martial arts

331
00:21:37,360 --> 00:21:39,690
and help you catch the mastermind behind.

332
00:21:40,190 --> 00:21:41,910
Your illness is not a big deal.

333
00:21:42,670 --> 00:21:44,730
You are still cute even with illness.

334
00:21:48,360 --> 00:21:51,190
Don't worry. I'm here.

335
00:21:55,110 --> 00:21:57,660
Let's drink.

336
00:22:05,330 --> 00:22:06,380
Are you done?

337
00:22:06,480 --> 00:22:09,070
Time to rest now.

338
00:22:26,310 --> 00:22:27,860
Are you okay?

339
00:22:31,790 --> 00:22:35,300
You are Wen Chenyi.

340
00:22:36,720 --> 00:22:40,270
♫The candle is burning out; The dawn is breaking♫

341
00:22:40,390 --> 00:22:42,470
I knew it.

342
00:22:40,510 --> 00:22:43,400
♫The moon knows my thoughts♫

343
00:22:43,510 --> 00:22:45,970
Only Wen Chenyi

344
00:22:44,150 --> 00:22:47,690
♫Life is so long, I hope to spend♫

345
00:22:46,990 --> 00:22:48,670
will be with me

346
00:22:48,080 --> 00:22:50,860
♫The rest of my life with you♫

347
00:22:49,630 --> 00:22:51,030
when I am in trouble

348
00:22:51,580 --> 00:22:53,950
and feel desperate.

349
00:22:51,640 --> 00:22:55,040
♫It's a long way to go♫

350
00:22:55,400 --> 00:22:58,110
Only Wen Chenyi will help me.

351
00:22:55,420 --> 00:23:04,750
♫May I have a lifelong partner♫

352
00:23:06,480 --> 00:23:09,910
♫Let me be your lover♫

353
00:23:07,830 --> 00:23:10,660
Did I say thank you to you?

354
00:23:10,150 --> 00:23:12,990
♫Hope you can get to know my love♫

355
00:23:13,510 --> 00:23:17,060
♫Wait for the arrangement of fate♫

356
00:23:17,300 --> 00:23:20,170
♫Let us be together♫

357
00:23:17,930 --> 00:23:20,480
Thank you. Thank you.

358
00:23:21,070 --> 00:23:24,590
♫It's a long way to go♫

359
00:23:24,860 --> 00:23:34,270
♫I want to be with you forever♫

360
00:23:27,260 --> 00:23:28,010
Actually,

361
00:23:28,870 --> 00:23:30,090
I should

362
00:23:31,160 --> 00:23:32,770
thank you.

363
00:23:34,690 --> 00:23:38,230
♫In halcyon days♫

364
00:23:38,650 --> 00:23:41,700
♫I can hug you♫

365
00:23:42,060 --> 00:23:45,600
♫And give you a happy life♫

366
00:23:45,950 --> 00:23:49,230
♫Let's hold hands and grow old together♫

367
00:23:49,660 --> 00:23:53,150
♫Let that story be sloppy♫

368
00:23:53,530 --> 00:23:56,650
♫It's worth the love♫

369
00:23:56,890 --> 00:24:00,300
♫It's good that it's you♫

370
00:24:00,510 --> 00:24:03,590
♫It's okay to be a little late♫

371
00:24:30,490 --> 00:24:31,110
Why…

372
00:24:31,140 --> 00:24:32,920
Why did I sleep here?

373
00:24:34,090 --> 00:24:35,850
Why did you sleep here?

374
00:24:35,980 --> 00:24:37,390
Let me think

375
00:24:37,430 --> 00:24:38,850
where to start.

376
00:24:45,820 --> 00:24:47,960
Yi, are you awake?

377
00:24:47,970 --> 00:24:49,760
I made chicken soup for you.

378
00:24:58,480 --> 00:24:59,430
Be careful.

379
00:25:15,400 --> 00:25:17,670
It's inappropriate to display your affection

380
00:25:17,670 --> 00:25:18,720
in public.

381
00:25:18,760 --> 00:25:21,540
You two should kneel in the ancestral hall as punishment.

382
00:25:21,540 --> 00:25:22,580
I'm sorry

383
00:25:22,610 --> 00:25:24,390
for involving you.

384
00:25:28,220 --> 00:25:30,130
Don't be angry.

385
00:25:31,200 --> 00:25:33,430
Think from another perspective.

386
00:25:33,460 --> 00:25:35,500
It's not necessarily a bad thing to kneel in the ancestral hall,

387
00:25:35,500 --> 00:25:38,700
especially for writers like you.

388
00:25:38,730 --> 00:25:40,210
You are experiencing life

389
00:25:40,230 --> 00:25:42,170
and accumulating materials for your writing.

390
00:25:42,170 --> 00:25:43,710
In that case,

391
00:25:44,950 --> 00:25:46,070
I should thank you.

392
00:25:47,550 --> 00:25:49,090
No worries.

393
00:25:49,490 --> 00:25:51,680
Just don't be angry.

394
00:25:54,840 --> 00:25:57,980
This is the first time you kneel in the ancestral hall, right?

395
00:25:57,980 --> 00:25:59,840
I've done many things for the first time

396
00:25:59,840 --> 00:26:01,280
because of you.

397
00:26:02,330 --> 00:26:03,080
Yes.

398
00:26:03,380 --> 00:26:05,670
But there are many beautiful memories.

399
00:26:06,260 --> 00:26:07,100
Like what?

400
00:26:08,020 --> 00:26:09,490
Like...

401
00:26:15,650 --> 00:26:16,570
Like…

402
00:26:16,670 --> 00:26:18,060
I saw nothing.

403
00:26:21,750 --> 00:26:23,220
And like…

404
00:26:30,350 --> 00:26:32,950
No, I cannot think about any beautiful memory.

405
00:26:33,430 --> 00:26:35,620
There have been some.

406
00:26:54,540 --> 00:26:55,780
What's wrong?

407
00:26:57,940 --> 00:26:58,820
I'm fine.

408
00:27:00,040 --> 00:27:02,090
Just some coldness inside my body.

409
00:27:02,110 --> 00:27:05,040
That's serious. Why are you still pretending tough?

410
00:27:12,610 --> 00:27:14,380
Wait here. I'll get someone.

411
00:27:21,180 --> 00:27:23,140
If you didn't punish Yi to kneel in the ancestral hall,

412
00:27:23,140 --> 00:27:24,760
he wouldn't have had a cough.

413
00:27:25,900 --> 00:27:27,590
My son suffered a lot.

414
00:27:28,030 --> 00:27:31,430
I'm afraid he'll have to spend his birthday in illness.

415
00:27:32,410 --> 00:27:33,830
Honey, calm down.

416
00:27:33,890 --> 00:27:34,890
Don't be sad.

417
00:27:34,920 --> 00:27:36,150
Yi

418
00:27:36,170 --> 00:27:37,450
is not greedy.

419
00:27:37,660 --> 00:27:39,120
He never celebrates his birthday.

420
00:27:39,120 --> 00:27:40,920
He won't be unhappy because of this.

421
00:27:40,920 --> 00:27:42,620
How could you say that?

422
00:27:42,640 --> 00:27:44,060
As his mom, I wish that

423
00:27:44,090 --> 00:27:45,300
he could spend his birthday

424
00:27:45,300 --> 00:27:46,860
in peace.

425
00:27:46,890 --> 00:27:49,260
Yes, you're right.

426
00:27:49,310 --> 00:27:52,070
I'll find the best doctor in the city to treat Yi.

427
00:27:52,170 --> 00:27:52,930
Hurry up.

428
00:28:09,800 --> 00:28:10,830
You're awake.

429
00:28:12,550 --> 00:28:13,900
Luckily, you're fine.

430
00:28:14,910 --> 00:28:16,100
Have you been taking care of me all the time?

431
00:28:16,100 --> 00:28:18,230
Who else can take care of you except me?

432
00:28:19,480 --> 00:28:21,430
I am exhausted

433
00:28:21,830 --> 00:28:23,160
for taking care of you.

434
00:28:25,430 --> 00:28:26,690
Thank you, Miss Cheng.

435
00:28:28,130 --> 00:28:30,530
How are you going to return me the favor?

436
00:28:32,340 --> 00:28:33,770
Is she

437
00:28:33,790 --> 00:28:35,340
coveting my body, isn't she?

438
00:28:35,340 --> 00:28:38,060
You're fully recovered, aren't you?

439
00:28:38,860 --> 00:28:39,660
I knew it.

440
00:28:41,820 --> 00:28:42,930
Yes.

441
00:28:43,160 --> 00:28:44,030
That's good.

442
00:28:45,850 --> 00:28:47,850
Get up. Get dressed and come with me.

443
00:28:55,470 --> 00:28:57,670
Why did you bring me here?

444
00:28:58,280 --> 00:29:00,520
Without doubt, to buy fabrics.

445
00:29:00,550 --> 00:29:02,910
Your task today is to be a model

446
00:29:02,940 --> 00:29:05,600
and help me pick out the most suitable style.

447
00:29:05,630 --> 00:29:06,950
Model?

448
00:29:07,730 --> 00:29:08,960
What is this?

449
00:29:09,560 --> 00:29:11,880
You need to

450
00:29:12,390 --> 00:29:17,300
put on the clothes and walk like this.

451
00:29:20,030 --> 00:29:21,110
Don't look. What are you doing?

452
00:29:21,110 --> 00:29:22,590
Go over there.

453
00:29:23,490 --> 00:29:24,650
Stop in front of me.

454
00:29:24,670 --> 00:29:27,390
Turn around clockwise and then counter-clockwise.

455
00:29:27,390 --> 00:29:28,520
Where are you going?

456
00:29:30,930 --> 00:29:32,250
I am in no mood

457
00:29:32,280 --> 00:29:33,440
to have fun with you.

458
00:29:33,820 --> 00:29:34,540
Goodbye.

459
00:29:34,760 --> 00:29:35,750
Stop there!

460
00:29:36,760 --> 00:29:39,080
You don't want to return the favor to me?

461
00:29:39,290 --> 00:29:41,600
I'm the Greatest Scholar of the Feng State.

462
00:29:41,600 --> 00:29:43,500
How could I do such a strange thing?

463
00:29:43,500 --> 00:29:44,700
It's inappropriate!

464
00:29:45,470 --> 00:29:46,930
As long as you're not afraid of being embarrassed,

465
00:29:46,930 --> 00:29:48,730
just walk out with your head high.

466
00:29:48,730 --> 00:29:50,790
I won't return the belt to you anyway.

467
00:29:50,830 --> 00:29:51,400
Give it to me.

468
00:29:51,400 --> 00:29:52,790
You won't win if we fight.

469
00:29:52,790 --> 00:29:53,590
Stop it.

470
00:29:54,870 --> 00:29:57,590
Sir, please show me all your fine fabrics.

471
00:29:57,630 --> 00:29:58,670
I can afford it.

472
00:29:59,030 --> 00:30:00,920
Guys, move!

473
00:30:01,190 --> 00:30:01,910
Yes.

474
00:30:03,270 --> 00:30:03,910
Cheng Manyi!

